  <!-- EN: wolfscarab -->
  <GR_Wolfscarab.label>狼甲虫</GR_Wolfscarab.label>
  <!-- EN: The answer to all your worries about escaping slaves. These omnivorous vicious beasties are effectively exotic hunting dogs, and the most exotic and forbidden prey of all is humans. That is, provided they’re practically unable to defend themselves. Everyone knows you can kill as many people as you like, just don’t hurt the poor puppy trying to tear your throat out.\n\nAn insectoid hybrid with recessive canine genes. Incredibly fast and with multiple hardened jaw plates, these ferocious hunting dogs make for an excellent, intelligent combat hybrid. Unable to take much punishment but the armour plating should help against those lacking in offensive weaponry.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color> All insectoid hybrids have good armor and no toxic sensitivity, but they are always sterile and can't reproduce, even if a fertility booster is used to create them. -->
  <GR_Wolfscarab.description>殖民地里的奴隶和囚犯总是伺机逃跑？别担心，这些杂食性的凶暴生物会让他们为这件事后悔终生！虽然身上的甲壳质防护作用有限，但极快的速度与锋利的口器能让它们轻易地撕裂那些毫无防备之敌的喉咙。\n\n【性状基因I】：虫族基因\n【性状基因II】：犬科基因\n【基本特征】：野性高，可训练度高，移动速度快。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C>游戏效果：&lt;/color>大部分虫族混种生物都拥有100%毒物抗性和一定护甲值。它们没有繁殖功能，在塑造孵化单元时加入生育解限剂也无济于事。</GR_Wolfscarab.description>
